Bump. Anyone here own this card?

SL = Southern Leaguer - a subset of 48 players that played in the Southern & Texas Leagues.  They were offered with 3 different backs - Old Mill(southern league specific OM back), Hindu & Piedmont 350 (Not all SLers are available in all 3 backs) - plus I guess the very rare blank backs.

Cory, thanks for answering!
